text: The building's exterior in 2007 Agen Warehouse is a building located at 1201 Western Avenue in Seattle, Washington. It was added to the National Register of Historic Places on January 23, 1998.http://focus.nps.gov/AssetDetail/NRIS/97001673 ==See also== * List of Seattle landmarks * National Register of Historic Places listings in Seattle, Washington ==References== ==External links== * Category:National Register of Historic Places in Seattle Category:Office buildings in Seattle Category:Commercial buildings on the National Register of Historic Places in Washington (state)
